Trinity::

She smiled and looked up at Aerotaur. "Yup. I'm ok."
She walked up to the pod and tried to jump up on top of the pod. She 
climbed up using some of the plants that still clung to the pod. She 
stood up on top of it and knocked on it with her paw. "HELLO! Anyone 
in there?"
